data.enText: the ability to control your thoughts and actions in order to achieve what you want to do

tr: the trait of resolutely controlling your own behavior

value.def: Willpower is a very strong determination to do something.

example.ex: I know I've got the willpower to do it...
example.tran: 我知道我有毅力做这事儿。

example.ex: His attempts to stop smoking by willpower alone failed.
example.tran: 他多次想单凭意志力戒烟都没有成功。
